                {
                  "type": "frame",
                  "id": "section-concepts",
                  "width": 768,
                  "height": 400,
                  "fill": "$sys/color.bg-200",
                  "border": {
                    "thickness": 1,
                    "fill": "$sys/color.border-300"
                  },
                  "cornerRadius": 12,
                  "padding": [24, 24, 24, 24],
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "concepts-title",
                      "content": "核心概念",
                      "fontSize": 28,
                      "fontWeight": "700",
                      "fill": "$sys/color.text-50"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "frame",
                      "id": "concept-1",
                      "layout": "vertical",
                      "gap": 8,
                      "y": 48,
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "concept-1-title",
                          "content": "Hook 注入机制",
                          "fontSize": 20,
                          "fontWeight": "600",
                          "fill": "$sys/color.text-50"
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "concept-1-desc",
                          "content": "在 SDK 工具调用（如 edit_file、run_command）时自动注入上下文提示，三级匹配粒度灵活控制 AI 行为，无需修改源码。",
                          "fontSize": 14,
                          "fontWeight": "400",
                          "fill": "$sys/color.text-400",
                          "lineHeight": 1.5
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "frame",
                      "id": "concept-2",
                      "layout": "vertical",
                      "gap": 8,
                      "y": 110,
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "concept-2-title",
                          "content": "Session 守护",
                          "fontSize": 20,
                          "fontWeight": "600",
                          "fill": "$sys/color.text-50"
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "concept-2-desc",
                          "content": "Harness 持续监控 Agent Session 状态，自动处理超时、中断、无响应。失败时 git 回滚 + 重试，确保长时间无人值守编码的稳定性。",
                          "fontSize": 14,
                          "fontWeight": "400",
                          "fill": "$sys/color.text-400",
                          "lineHeight": 1.5
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "frame",
                      "id": "concept-3",
                      "layout": "vertical",
                      "gap": 8,
                      "y": 172,
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "concept-3-title",
                          "content": "任务分解与编排",
                          "fontSize": 20,
                          "fontWeight": "600",
                          "fill": "$sys/color.text-50"
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "concept-3-desc",
                          "content": "将复杂需求拆分为独立子任务，按依赖关系排序。每个 Session 执行 6 步流程：恢复上下文 → 环境检查 → 选任务 → 编码 → 测试 → 收尾。",
                          "fontSize": 14,
                          "fontWeight": "400",
                          "fill": "$sys/color.text-400",
                          "lineHeight": 1.5
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                },
