                              "type": "text",
                              "id": "issue-3-title",
                              "content": "长时间无响应",
                              "fontSize": 20,
                              "fontWeight": "600",
                              "fill": "$sys/color.text-50"
                            },
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "id": "issue-3-desc",
                              "content": "模型处理复杂任务时可能出现长思考间隔，这是正常行为。超过阈值后 Harness 自动中断并重试。可通过 SESSION_STALL_TIMEOUT 调整。",
                              "fontSize": 14,
                              "fontWeight": "400",
                              "fill": "$sys/color.text-400",
                              "lineHeight": 1.5
                            }
                          ]
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
